    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I see. So if the structure itself is fundamentally flawed because of those power dynamics, would you say the whole concept of a collective security system like the UN is actually practical, or is it just an outdated ideal that doesn't really work in the real world anymore?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
